body:
If this were 2 seasons ago, when Zyra was OP as hell before they nerfed her out of mid lane completely, then yes, I would be fine with people telling me things like &quot;Zyra ez&quot; &quot;your damage doesn&#039;t count you&#039;re zyra&quot; ...etc

But it&#039;s not.
Welcome to 2018, where Zyra&#039;s plants are 1 shotable by most classes, where to get your plants to even attack enemy team you have to land your w &amp; q simultaneously on the exact location of an enemy champ, or get close enough to auto attack range and hope you can auto attack them once, after dropping your plants, so your plants focus the enemy team instead of the enemies minions, in which case your adc starts screaming at you for your plants &quot;stealing his cs&quot;

So yeah, don&#039;t tell me I didn&#039;t earn my S+. Don&#039;t tell me I didn&#039;t earn having double my entire teams damage to enemy champions.{{champion:143}}
